  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A DROP OF WATER, A SAVED OF LIFE</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water been a necessity of life, shall become a problem solved in Amoanda community. Citizen will have their separate source of drinking water while animals will share streams only for themselves.  The issue of humans sharing the same streams with animals will become a thing of the past. Lives of humans shall become healthier and better living conditions shall be improved.   Funding the drilling of a bore-hole water facility in Amoanda  will help solve the current water crisis Amoanda.</narrative>
  </description>
